 <instruction>das sewd uil gar so</instruction>
 <instruction>nym dann <ingredient en="white bread" commodity="Q1501889">weiss prott</ingredient> <ingredient en="ginger" commodity="Q15046077">Ingwers</ingredient> mer denn <ingredient en="pepper" commodity="Q3143131">pheffers</ingredient> <ingredient en="anise" commodity="Q33873455">Aneyzz</ingredient> <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">Saffran</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>das mal mit <ingredient en="vinegar" commodity="Q41354">essaech</ingredient> vnd mit dunnen <ingredient en="beer" commodity="Q44">pier</ingredient> nicht zu Sawr</instruction>
 <instruction>mit disem <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">Condiment</dish> Sewd die <dish en="aspic" commodity="Q837480">Sulcz</dish> vollen gar</instruction>
 . <instruction>leg sy In ein <tool en="barrel" commodity="Q10289">vas</tool></instruction>
 <instruction>gews das <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">Codiment</dish> darauff</instruction>
 <closer>das haisst . <name>Lamparttisch <dish en="aspic" commodity="Q837480">Sulcz</dish></name></closer> </div></body></text></TEI>